{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place 30 g sugar in mixing bowl and grind <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place egg whites in mixing bowl then whisk <b>without setting a time\/speed 3.5<b> until soft peaks form, watching carefully to avoid over-whisking. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place 80 g sugar, flour, cream, salt and egg yolks in mixing bowl then mix <b>1 min\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides and base of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add reserved whisked egg whites and fold in <b>15 sec\/speed 3<b>.","Preheat oven to 200°C. Meanwhile, add butter and remaining 40 g sugar to an oven-proof frying pan over a medium heat. Add rhubarb and cook for approx. 5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until soft and starting to lose shape. Add flaked almonds then fry for a further 1-2 minutes.","Pour batter over rhubarb in frying pan, then mix together gently. Bake in oven for 10 minutes (200°C). Set aside to cool for 15 minutes.","Using two spoons or forks, pull pancakes apart creating little rhubarb pieces. Dust with reserved icing sugar before serving warm or cold."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["150 g sugar","3 large eggs, separated","70 g plain flour","200 g double cream","1 pinch fine sea salt","30 g butter","500 g rhubarb, cut in pieces (3 cm)","40 g flaked almonds"]}],"id":"r103533","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-nS97tNxyNwQ\/XZWdfEwnKcI\/AAAAAAAAemI\/WYELU_B9dvgaKxn3l5mvj3brhxoWqgQwQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_HIDpcr6jUeXbbBPE.png","title":"Rhubarb Pancake Pieces","publishedAt":"2016-05-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"10.9 g","fat":"40.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"56.1 g","calories":"2655 kJ \/ 635 kcal"},"usefulItems":"oven-proof frying pan, cooling rack, soft spatula, oven, hob","hintsAndTricks":["Fresh gooseberries or cherries also work well in place of rhubarb.","Instead of almonds you can use pistachios."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","50m","4 portions"]}